    90→### Build Swap Calls (for multicall composition)
    91→
    92→```typescript
    93→import { quoteToCalls } from "@avnu/avnu-sdk";
    94→
    95→const calls = await quoteToCalls({
    96→  quote: bestQuote,
    97→  takerAddress: account.address,
    98→  slippage: 0.01,
    99→  includeApprove: true,
   100→});
   101→// `calls` can be combined with other calls in account.execute([...calls, ...otherCalls])
